    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重要说明：</strong>请注意，Hacker Simulator<strong>并不是</strong>对现实黑客行为的1:1真实模拟，游戏机制仅<strong><u>借鉴</u></strong>了现实中的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Hacker Simulator</strong>中，我希望带来一段有趣且沉浸的黑客主题体验，让您对其中的一些方面有更直观的认识（由于我独自开发，当然不可能面面俱到）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/c600c967c4ff8c9f0c380d5f66cda869.poster.avif?t=1769519847\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/c600c967c4ff8c9f0c380d5f66cda869.webm?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/c600c967c4ff8c9f0c380d5f66cda869.mp4?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了让您的业务持续运转，您需要经常保持匿名，隐藏在不同的 Wi-Fi 网络之后。为此，您将学习使用著名的工具套件<strong>Aircrack-ng</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/905abac75db825bb393357c36c1f8748.poster.avif?t=1769519847\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/905abac75db825bb393357c36c1f8748.webm?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/905abac75db825bb393357c36c1f8748.mp4?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们做了大量研究，为您呈现现实黑客方法的简化且友好的版本，例如<strong>暴力破解</strong>、<strong>漏洞利用</strong>、<strong>网络钓鱼</strong>等！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/1a6088018c13d9c210e3eb4587bf23bb.poster.avif?t=1769519847\" width=610 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/1a6088018c13d9c210e3eb4587bf23bb.webm?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1754840/extras/1a6088018c13d9c210e3eb4587bf23bb.mp4?t=1769519847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在冒险过程中，您会学到很多，同时也会认识到黑客行为并非没有风险。您将探索的网络将被<u>加固</u>，Wi-Fi 连接将被<u>监控</u>，因此需要保持高度警惕。</p>",
